+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

PrBoom-Plus can run in several game modes.

Doom shareware is available in the doomdata package.  One or more
registered IWADs may be placed in ${PREFIX}/share/doom/.

Doom, Ultimate Doom, Doom II: Hell on Earth, and Final Doom are
supported.

If multiple IWADs are installed, you may specify the one you want to
play via the -iwad command-line parameter e.g.

  $ prboom-plus -iwad doom.wad

Music is available with the timidity package.
